name: Ishimwe Frank
subject: Samples inquiry!
message:
Hi Baho Team,
I hope this message finds you well. I'm interested in learning more about your products and would like to request samples to explore potential opportunities with your brand.
Could you please let me know what samples are available and what information you'd need from me to process this request? I'm happy to provide any details about my business or intended use.
Thank you for your time, and I look forward to hearing from you.
Best regards,
Frank Ishimwe
Marketing/Baho Coffee
